%pyspark
from string import Template
from collections import defaultdict
from SPARQLWrapper import SPARQLWrapper, JSON
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns

import urllib2
proxy = urllib2.ProxyHandler({'http': 'gateway.ad.renci.org:8080'})
opener = urllib2.build_opener(proxy)
urllib2.install_opener(opener)

blazegraph_uri = "http://stars-blazegraph.renci.org/bigdata/sparql"
blazegraph = SPARQLWrapper (blazegraph_uri)
def query_sparql (query, service=blazegraph):
    service.setQuery (query)
    service.setReturnFormat (JSON)
    return service.query().convert ()

%pyspark

query = Template ("""
PREFIX db_resource: <http://chem2bio2rdf.org/drugbank/resource/>
SELECT ?subject ?predicate ?object
WHERE {?subject ?predicate ?object}Â 
LIMIT 100""")
results = query_sparql (query)

PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> 
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> 
PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> 
PREFIX obo: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/> 
PREFIX cebs: <http://cebs.niehs.nih.gov/cebs/> 
PREFIX sift: <http://cebs.niehs.nih.gov/sift/> 

SELECT DISTINCT ?subject ?subject_label (STR(?organ_type_label) as ?organ_name) (STR(?morphology_type_label) as ?morphology_name) 
WHERE { VALUES ?organ_root { obo:UBERON_0013765 # digestive system element obo:UBERON_0000020 # sense organ } 
GRAPH ?m1 { ?subject a cebs:subject; rdfs:label ?subject_label . ?organ a ?organ_type ; obo:BFO_0000050 ?subject . # part of } 
GRAPH ?m2 { ?morphology a ?morphology_type ; rdfs:label ?morphology_label ; obo:RO_0000052 ?organ . # inheres in } 
GRAPH sift:ontology { ?organ_type rdfs:subClassOf* ?organ_root ; rdfs:label ?organ_type_label . ?morphology_type rdfs:label ?morphology_type_label . } } LIMIT 100
